nbwmon
======
Ncurses bandwidth monitor.

Features
--------
* Print bandwidth graphs.
* Print current, average and maximum transfer speeds.
* Print total traffic.
* Scale to full window on startup and resize.
* Detect active network interface.
* Support for multiple units.
* Support for colors.

Usage
-----
usage: nbwmon [options]

-h    help
-v    version
-n    no colors
-s    use SI units
-S    hide graph scale
-u    unified graph max

-i <interface>    network interface
-d <seconds>      redraw delay
-l <lines>        fixed graph height
